boilerplate -  a code template that can be reused (programming)

atom shortcuts - https://github.com/nwinkler/atom-keyboard-shortcuts


1.Character interpretation by web browser
->you can change the browser interpretation in order to decode correctly the text
-> utf-8/unicode uses international symbols
-> unicode also includes emojis

unicode interpretation info - https://www.fileformat.info/info/charset/UTF-8/list.htm

2. Use of style text
instead of using <i>(italics), <b>(bold) which only styles the text without any emphasis,
use <em>,<strong> to indicate that the text is important
